items.title: Awesome Wordpress Gatsby
items.content_text:
### WordPress / Essential Plugins

*   [WPGraphQL (⭐3.7k)](https://github.com/wp-graphql/wp-graphql) - [Documentation](https://docs.wpgraphql.com/) - WPGraphQL brings the power of GraphQL to your WordPress site.

### WordPress / WPGraphQL Extensions

*   [WPGraphQL Gutenberg (⭐305)](https://github.com/pristas-peter/wp-graphql-gutenberg) - Exposes Gutenberg blocks to the WPGraphQL API.
*   [WPGraphQL JWT Authentication (⭐349)](https://github.com/wp-graphql/wp-graphql-jwt-authentication) - Extends the WPGraphQL plugin to provide authentication using JWT (JSON Web Tokens).
*   [WPGraphQL Lock (⭐24)](https://github.com/valu-digital/wp-graphql-lock) - Enables query locking for WPGraphQL by implementing persisted GraphQL queries.
*   [QL Search (⭐13)](https://github.com/funkhaus/ql-search) - An extension that integrates SearchWP into WPGraphQL.
items.content_html:
WordPress / Essential Plugins

  • WPGraphQL (⭐3.7k) - Documentation - WPGraphQL brings the power of GraphQL to your WordPress site.

WordPress / WPGraphQL Extensions

  • WPGraphQL Gutenberg (⭐305) - Exposes Gutenberg blocks to the WPGraphQL API.
  • WPGraphQL JWT Authentication (⭐349) - Extends the WPGraphQL plugin to provide authentication using JWT (JSON Web Tokens).
  • WPGraphQL Lock (⭐24) - Enables query locking for WPGraphQL by implementing persisted GraphQL queries.
  • QL Search (⭐13) - An extension that integrates SearchWP into WPGraphQL.
